description:
Today on the show we had Lynn Richardson on the line where she spoke about On Maintaining Financial Stability, Overcoming Recession Setbacks and more. Also Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a couple that new they were Covid positive and still went on a flight to Hawaii and Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
